<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<Defs>
    <StatDef>
        <defName>SHG_FearSusceptibility</defName>
        <label>fear susceptibility</label>
        <description>How well this creature resists fear caused by the Superhero Genes mod. The lower this is, the less susceptibile the pawn is to fear.\n\nThis will have a different effect depending on what the source is. If the fear source is an ability, then this impacts how long the ability lasts for that particular pawn. If the source is a damaging attack, then this will influence how much fear increases per attack.</description>
        <category>BasicsPawn</category>
        <defaultBaseValue>1</defaultBaseValue>
        <hideAtValue>1</hideAtValue>
        <minValue>0</minValue>
        <toStringStyle>PercentZero</toStringStyle>
        <displayPriorityInCategory>3452</displayPriorityInCategory>
    </StatDef>

    <HediffDef Name="SHGFearBase">
        <defName>SHG_Fear</defName>
        <label>fear</label>
        <description>This pawn is suffering from the effects of an ability or attack infused with psychic energy that causes fear. This accelerates the heart, but may lead to may lead to irrational actions and, in very extreme cases, a risk of heart failure. The more fear a pawn is subjected to, the more unpredictable they become. If they are subjected to too much fear, then they will be trapped in their mind for some time, and be completely incapable of moving.</description>
        <hediffClass>HediffWithComps</hediffClass>
        <maxSeverity>1</maxSeverity>
        <stages>
            <li>
                <label>twitchy</label>
                <minSeverity>0.01</minSeverity>
